<h2>install</h2>
<h3>MemberOf</h3>
<p>```bash</p>
<h1>Activate</h1>
<p>ldapmodify -Y EXTERNAL -H ldapi:/// &lt;&lt;EOF
dn: cn=module{0},cn=config
changetype: modify
add: olcModuleLoad
